--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: e9620f8c34305754d8cc9a7e49e852d9, type: 3}
  m_Name: BossIntro_en
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  m_LocaleId:
    m_Code: en
  m_SharedData: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 5c2851b8a68d6754891926623da71de0, type: 2}
  m_Metadata:
    m_Items: []
  m_TableData:
  - m_Id: 56416882688
    m_Localized: "Boo! \u2026Welcome, Jackson."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 282867355648
    m_Localized: "This one\u2019s a bit\u2026 unusual. He\u2019s obsessed with trump
      cards."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 286096969728
    m_Localized: "He decides everything\u2026 by card suits."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 289578242048
    m_Localized: "Boo! You\u2019ll see the suit above his head"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 292841410560
    m_Localized: "Hearts, clubs, spades, diamonds \u2014\neach one has a different
      attack pattern, so stay sharp."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 295760646144
    m_Localized: "And remember something called the stack. It\u2019s important."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 297966850048
    m_Localized: "If the stack reaches 7\u2026 the clown will kill you."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 299673931776
    m_Localized: "Boo! First up \u2014 hearts. Among several boxes,\nyou\u2019ll
      have to find the clown hiding inside one of them."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 301401985024
    m_Localized: "More stacks mean more boxes\u2026 so watch closely."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 303079706624
    m_Localized: "Boo! For clubs, a spinning wheel will appear \u2014\naim for the
      \u201C-\u201D or \u201C0\u201D.\nIf you hit \u201C+\u201D, the stack increases
      by that number!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 304912617472
    m_Localized: "Boo! For spades, he\u2019ll throw cards at you \u2014 shoot them
      down!\nIf you hit them, something good might happen."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 306691002368
    m_Localized: "Boo! Diamonds mean teleportation \u2014\nthe boss will warp around,
      and you\u2019ll have to hit him 5 times to avoid getting hurt."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 308574244864
    m_Localized: "Boo! Well then\u2026 good luck. Hehe\u2026"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1427270619136
    m_Localized: "Boo! Amazing\u2026 I knew you could do it."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1428747014144
    m_Localized: "But this next one is\u2026 dangerous. He\u2019s\u2026"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1430156300288
    m_Localized: "No, it\u2019s something that hates rock itself."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1431733358592
    m_Localized: Loud! Unstable! Just imagining it drives you mad!
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1434619039744
    m_Localized: "Boo! Oh\u2014 sorry. That\u2019s just something it says all the
      time. Don\u2019t mind me. Definitely not my own opinion\u2026"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1436028325888
    m_Localized: Let me explain again. Listen carefully.
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1437743796224
    m_Localized: "Boo! The boss will scatter energy bullets around the field.\nThey\u2019ll
      come flying at you in the same order they were fired \u2014\nso keep track
      and destroy them in rhythm!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1439316660224
    m_Localized: "Boo! Then, he\u2019ll throw energy orbs from above \u2014\nyou\u2019ll
      need to shoot them down or avoid them entirely."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 1440725946368
    m_Localized: 'Boo! After a while, the boss will glow red,

      summon small
      enemies, and his patterns will power up.

      Be extremely careful when that
      happens...'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2041853595648
    m_Localized: Boo... Welcome back... had a rough time, huh?
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2043325796352
    m_Localized: "Jackson\u2026 thanks to you, I have less work to do now."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2044663779328
    m_Localized: "But there\u2019s one last thing left."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2046026928128
    m_Localized: "Boo... Come closer\u2026 toward that picture frame."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2047461380096
    m_Localized: "Boo! What\u2019s wrong? Did you forget I\u2019m a ghost too?"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2048933580800
    m_Localized: "At first, stealing and returning rock was just a little prank\u2026\nbut
      then\u2026 I lost that intention completely."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2050313506816
    m_Localized: "Feeling powerless! Losing will! Watching people treat rock like
      their entire lives\u2014\nit drove me insane!"
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2051655684096
    m_Localized: 'Unlike the fools trapped inside their frames,

      I became the
      king of both the framed world and the real one!'
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  - m_Id: 2052859449344
    m_Localized: "Jackson, I owe you thanks\u2026\nSo as a reward, I\u2019ll grant
      you the honor of becoming my first sacrifice."
    m_Metadata:
      m_Items: []
  references:
    version: 2
    RefIds: []
